node.text:
“a lot had happened right? there were many complications, and many things that happened, and that moment we were so worried about all of you. with your worried hearts we did not want to let you feel more hurt, that was what i thought about a lot. honestly my thoughts are really not organised now... i just don’t want to ever leave everyone, and i’ll keep working hard (pause) but there were more walls than i expected, i just want to have fun and keep going with everyone but there’s something constantly blocking and i am so tired. so everyone,... please don’t go anywhere, you have to stay by my side, i’ll keep working hard to become a stray kids that you won’t be embarrassed of, thank you.”
